snippet.title: Cuphead - The Delicious Last Course - Introducing Ms. Chalice - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Get ready to dine with Cuphead, Mugman & Ms. Chalice when Cuphead - The Delicious Last Course expansion comes to Nintendo Switch on June 30!

Tackle a bevy of new bosses in #CupheadDLC using exciting new weapons and charms, and Ms. Chalice’s unique abilities! 

Learn more: http://www.cupheadgame.com/dlc.html

#CupheadDLC #NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch
